```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as Django API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FS as File Storage
    participant Celery as Celery Worker
    participant OCR as OCR Provider
    participant Claude as Claude API (optional)
    actor Accountant

    Note over Client,Accountant: Document Upload → OCR → Extraction → Accountant Review

    Client->>FE: Opens /client/documents
    FE->>API: GET /api/portal/client/documents/
    API->>DB: SELECT documents WHERE engagement_id=X
    DB-->>API: document list
    API-->>FE: [{id, filename, status, confidence}, ...]
    FE-->>Client: Document list with status badges

    Client->>FE: Selects file + enters title + note
    FE->>API: POST /api/portal/client/documents/ (multipart)
    API->>API: Validate MIME type (PDF/JPEG/PNG/HEIC/CSV/XLSX)
    API->>API: Validate file size (max 20MB)

    alt Invalid file
        API-->>FE: 400 Bad Request {code: INVALID_FILE_TYPE}
        FE-->>Client: Error toast
    else Valid file
        API->>FS: Store file at media/portal/documents/{uuid}
        API->>DB: INSERT ClientDocument (status=uploaded)
        API->>DB: INSERT PortalAuditLog (action=document_uploaded)
        API-->>FE: 201 Created {id, status: "uploaded"}
        FE-->>Client: Upload success toast

        Note over API,Celery: Async OCR pipeline starts
        API->>Celery: enqueue extract_document_task(document_id)

        Celery->>FS: Read file bytes
        Celery->>OCR: Submit document for OCR
        OCR-->>Celery: Raw text + layout
        Celery->>DB: UPDATE ClientDocument (status=processing)

        Note over Celery,Claude: Optional AI-assisted field extraction
        Celery->>Claude: "Extract fields from this jaaropgaaf: {raw_text}"
        Claude-->>Celery: {gross_salary: 72000, tax_withheld: 14000, confidence: 0.87}

        Celery->>DB: INSERT ExtractedIncome (review_status=candidate, confidence=0.87)
        Celery->>DB: INSERT ExtractedField per field (field_key, raw_value, confidence, bounding_box)

        alt Overall confidence >= 0.90
            Celery->>DB: UPDATE ClientDocument (status=classified)
        else Confidence < 0.90
            Celery->>DB: UPDATE ClientDocument (status=needs_review)
            Celery->>DB: INSERT AccountantAction (type=review_required, stable_key=...)
        end

        Celery->>API: Trigger readiness recalculation
        API->>DB: recalculate_readiness(engagement_id)
        DB-->>API: new_score=72
        API->>DB: UPDATE TaxEngagement (readiness_score=72)
        API->>DB: INSERT PortalAuditLog (action=readiness_updated)
    end

    Note over Accountant,DB: Accountant reviews low-confidence extraction
    Accountant->>FE: Opens /accountant/engagements/{id} → Documents tab
    FE->>API: GET /api/portal/engagements/{id}/documents/
    API-->>FE: [{id, status: "needs_review", confidence: 0.72, ...}]
    FE-->>Accountant: Document list with "Needs Review" badge

    Accountant->>FE: Clicks document → opens split panel
    FE->>API: GET /api/portal/documents/{id}/extraction/
    API-->>FE: {fields: [{key, raw_value, confidence, bounding_box}, ...]}
    FE-->>Accountant: Split panel: document preview + field review table

    Accountant->>FE: Corrects gross_salary from 5800 to 58800
    Accountant->>FE: Clicks "Approve with corrections"
    FE->>API: POST /api/portal/engagements/{id}/document-reviews/{rid}/decision
    Note right of FE: {decision: "approve_with_corrections", fieldDecisions: [...]}

    API->>DB: UPDATE ExtractedField (corrected_value=58800, review_state=corrected)
    API->>DB: UPDATE ExtractedIncome (gross_salary=58800, review_status=approved)
    API->>DB: UPDATE ClientDocument (status=approved)
    API->>DB: INSERT PortalAuditLog (action=extraction_reviewed, reviewer=Sara)
    API->>API: recalculate_readiness(engagement_id)
    API->>DB: UPDATE TaxEngagement (readiness_score=82)
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {decision: "approve_with_corrections", readiness: {before:72, after:82}}
    FE-->>Accountant: Success toast + readiness ring updates to 82
```
